"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"> 邱立波. 趋势技术分析\\\\[M\\\\]. 中国宇航出版社, 2013.\\n\\n> 趋势线、压力线（支撑线）、通道，的应用；道氏理论与技术分析的集中体现\\n\\n### 1、道氏理论是趋势分析的基础\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/iY0Ur7oWAP05zsuBxyGnI.png?height=118&width=1327)\\n\\n牛熊判断：\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/uezMpEpxYZz3NlYSrp4vk.png?height=776&width=1197)\\n\\n趋势分为长、中、短：\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/drfNf7Mlu1776lNkmrB5T.png?height=771&width=1191)\\n\\n### 2、左侧交易与右侧交易\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/SRqkOegeCXLfzj-qNGBEa.png?height=175&width=1327)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fFsBMquIKsnKIwVJlaisZ.png?height=766&width=1192)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/OMDbu_Rt7b_jacrEKRXcK.png?height=823&width=1198)\\n\\n### 3、仓位管理\\n\\n跟随趋势加仓：\\n\\n![随趋势加仓](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/vDLycXKenJzNYYehPErCA.png?height=773&width=1208)\\n\\n![随趋势减仓](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zxetA-wO5KmutkGELxiut.png?height=765&width=1184)\\n\\n有不利信号，就要减仓，哪怕减错了，还可以加回来：\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/gpLIxbmZha1w4N78tNgeV.png?height=769&width=1193)\\n\\n### 4、趋势线是判断趋势的主要手段\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/QwHrmUgx1CFDOf9ODfqna.png?height=171&width=1342)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/YqecJnZQn7KX-FRHTVsXJ.png?height=713&width=1199)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/g7ha1ivvfFhVMXpA40cxA.png?height=703&width=1184)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zMpyhUUgbGJJr8aOt5_r8.png?height=122&width=1337)\\n\\n不同周期的趋势线：\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/BK_A1dw-RMeg1JkGij3-O.png?height=712&width=1199)\\n\\n趋势与牛顿定律：\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JGAzkwPKkewv7JQ2QRZS1.png?height=755&width=624)\\n\\n趋势线的修正：\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_50EVsdG_IH5H4JoI5_bh.png?height=710&width=1199)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/DssFvjQM444ZQzn4jtUFm.png?height=705&width=1189)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/K6YpEL1BlYpu6IaQOomx2.png?height=174&width=1332)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/y88oUX6Huk2Tq89KKQEUE.png?height=709&width=1192)\\n\\n趋势线的应用（结合K线组合形态、均线，一起判断进场点、离场点）\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/nmhnRvAU5t90Rgg3yaAP0.png?height=698&width=1181)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/adtlkan22UQOWE1jETwK-.png?height=706&width=1189)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/knNsab0YcCzZvlND7nh7H.png?height=708&width=1191)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zoxN1EGQTHyVEMpydRg-N.png?height=711&width=1196)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/hnW8kBqwuj_q1tSDuh5qB.png?height=763&width=1208)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Te2o239-68dRdBXezik8u.png?height=702&width=1183)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/lEKSz68ul5k46NDtww_Pe.png?height=700&width=1182)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ASiBRgGFHEHBc4v1uEaSL.png?height=703&width=1189)\\n\\n![接上图](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/hcWF_sC_S2Wg_T3597iVc.png?height=705&width=1188)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Vv5IVS9CN0gmIXCLDHBJL.png?height=703&width=1189)\\n\\n### 5、支撑线与压力线\\n\\n支撑线与压力线常常是通道图形的边线，他们有可能转化为趋势线。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Jhi9Wdh4qxdH3XHtAMXKD.png?height=124&width=1368)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Wopy1re95i5iRYdYLT9WN.png?height=125&width=1350)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9fVI1WVS3zGkJ27lOPfKu.png?height=777&width=1203)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/wL7ZeEvBLpuwfYYNuUS3T.png?height=404&width=1341)\\n\\n支撑线（压力线）仍具有较强的支撑（压力）作用，但对于趋势的改变只能看趋势线。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_emL46-1AqC4mYuml203d.png?height=767&width=1191)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Akmpf048ksnxl6eYJ6W-2.png?height=768&width=1186)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8dS8FqmHFg8ZZwyLPrkyJ.png?height=227&width=1332)\\n\\n### 6、通道\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/BFQBjs8Py-U0AajDHWdRA.png?height=116&width=1343)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/E2s2JdnvpxckY79Ho0H85.png?height=283&width=1327)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zmOme0QCfHx05F5yZAPCS.png?height=768&width=1191)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/F9f74SMl8vqnuCoTPQPfq.png?height=109&width=1332)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/afByM7bVhBnOuXrA6NFvk.png?height=771&width=1197)\\n\\n通道逆推（可以提前大致确定趋势线）\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WCodl5qaaNum__iAIrISQ.png?height=766&width=1186)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/7zEvB2Ypxt7-hkrGMQ_Cc.png?height=776&width=1206)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641999361,\"title\":\"Kody读书室 ）交易技术系列 <<趋势技术分析>>\"},\"digest\":\"hkiyru1hHE-F2Xyt4nX0ArmSS7Jm45FAAS6rKemyvuo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x3438486F01506c43EDA084BF2f60ad6fAd24f0E5\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"alg\\\":\\\"ES256\\\",\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2tAcZA0lPIoVF7hlIZBNMf_nigaJJQE2QWRtFybmH6M\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"TlCl_5cGyRIt7c-1FKmA2FtfDgpSBPzo-mGjfOgO09o\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"mipcm--oPgnZ89gP_mLL9k5wgHd3c7uJDMTFSxtL-lF7YY12wDCXejpGtg1bKmObkWKtxdhMcQfk0b1jW8E_vQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x495970a5db0f31a8df72df9c5e826743ffc6b3a39fb5b5c2eb72f530f0c2fdee5c67b16b5d9c60a7b195423e7441d332aac1766d873571ed3290acc303f50c3c1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this d